ALTER USER "GROUP8" QUOTA UNLIMITED ON "NAVN PÃ… tablespace"
ALTER USER "GROUP8" QUOTA UNLIMITED ON indxg8;

CREATE TABLESPACE indxg8
DATAFILE 'u01/app/oracle/oradata/WOLCOTTDB/indxg8.dbf' SIZE 10M AUTOEXTEND ON;

After moving the tables into the tablespaces we created, all the indexes have the status unusable. Because the row'ids have changed after moving the tables
and needs to be rebuilt.

After rebuilding the indexes into a seperate tablespace they are all valid.

ALTER INDEX group404.cause.pk REBUILD TABLESPACE indxg8;





